claims:
15. A method for determining the mass to charge ratio of aerosol particles, dusts, and other microparticles and/or nanoparticles, the method comprising:
creating a focused stream of micro or nanoparticles;
trapping a single particle at a time from the focused stream in an electrostatic trap;
while the single particle is trapped, sensing, in real time, the amplitude and frequency of the oscillation of the single particle, and determining the mass to charge ratio of the single particle from the amplitude and frequency of oscillation.
